<br>
I am an Agnostic Erudite Magician, named Montagor.<br>
<br>
I am roleplaying a self-imposed exile from Erudin right now.  In brief, Montagor fell in love with a Heratic, brought her home to his parents, and they did not approve.  She killed herself the same night, and in bitterness, Montagor left Erudin.<br>
<br>
Perhaps some of his family would eventually come looking for him... that would make for some excellent roleplay.<br>
<br>
I'm mainly on at night and in the evenings, especially very late.  I'm in America, AZ time zone. (MST.)<br>
