Could it be they discovered some ancient writings which were extremely dangerous?  Either they were killed to silence them, or they went adventuring to try to accomplish something (a quest which some of us might take up).  If there's interest in coming up with some story arcs involving our family, this could be an excellent opportunity (you can only kill off your parents once, generally). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uincandescent.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Incandescent</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/16/01 5:54:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmm...</span><hr size=1> Since Meralith (Montagor's wife/lover before she commit suicide) has been gone, Montagor hasn't seen his family at all.  He has ties with both sides, although is currently closer to his  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uincandescent.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Incandescent</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/16/01 5:57:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wha?</span><hr size=1> That keeps happening to me - my posts are getting cut off.<br>
