<br>
Ammdayan is the last remaining member of the house of Gadrieldor, a Heretic family.  Actually, last member isn't technically accurate as his parents still serve as guards of Paineel.  Ammdayan couldn't point them out though, as the necromancers assign new names to everything they raise...  Anyway, the Gadrieldor family was remarkably open-minded as far as Erudites go.  They recognized that most people, even the children of light and non-Erudites, can be honorable and worthy of respect.  They treated everybody as equals, though they never actually strayed from the teachings of Cazic-Thule through fear of the Faceless.<br>
<br>
This could be why they ended up as guards of Paineel.<br>
<br>
Ammdayan, a loyal cleric of fear, embraces the views of his parents, though he will never actively help a child of light out of fear for his Lord Cazic.  Because of this, he does not trust even the friendly smiles of his own fellow Heretics, and as nobody else will trust him, his life is a constant search for friendship in a harsh world.<br>
<br>
While I can't be an actual member of your family tree, I would be glad to be adopted into the Heretic branch of the family.  Or just establish friendships with either side of the family.  Ammdayan needs friends--desperately.  I figured this would be as good a place as any to look. <p>-----<BR>
Ammdayan<BR>
Loyal Cleric of Fear<BR>
